Acked-by: Patrik Jakobsson <pjakobsson@suse.de>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/vc4/vc4_crtc.c |  4 ++--
 drivers/gpu/drm/vc4/vc4_drv.h  |  9 +++++++++
 drivers/gpu/drm/vc4/vc4_hvs.c  | 12 ++++++++++++
 drivers/gpu/drm/vc4/vc4_txp.c  |  1 +
